# AinOne Dashboard — example environment file.
# Copy to `.env` (or `.env.local`) and fill in values that apply to you.
# All variables are optional; sensible defaults are baked into the code.
#
# The Hono backend loads `.env` automatically on boot via Node's native
# `process.loadEnvFile` (see backend/claude/cli/node.ts:loadEnvFiles).

# --- Claude (Hono) backend ---
# Path to the `claude` CLI executable. The Hono backend probes the standard
# Anthropic install locations automatically; only set this if your CLI lives
# elsewhere.
# CLAUDE_CLI_PATH=C:/Users/you/.local/bin/claude.exe

# Override the port the Claude (Hono) backend listens on (default 3000).
# PORT=3000

# Toggle verbose Hono debug logging.
# DEBUG=true

# --- Optional MiniMax MCP integration (off by default) ---
# Set MINIMAX_API_KEY to enable the MiniMax MCP server inside chat.
# Without a key, the chat handler registers no MCP servers.
# MINIMAX_API_HOST=https://api.minimaxi.com
# MINIMAX_API_KEY=

# --- Anthropic credentials (read by the Claude CLI itself) ---
# Most users configure these in `~/.claude/settings.json` instead.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=

# --- Diary agent secrets (v1.1.3+) ---
# Referenced from agents.json env blocks as `${NAME}`. Lookup order is:
#   agents.json secrets > process.env > literal placeholder kept.
# UI paste in Settings → Diary → Secrets always wins; values here are a
# fallback so users who prefer NOT to keep keys in agents.json can stash
# them here instead and skip the API-key paste step.
#
# Provider                  Variable name         Get it at
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Anthropic native          ANTHROPIC_KEY         console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# DeepSeek                  DEEPSEEK_KEY          platform.deepseek.com/api_keys
# MiniMax (intl/cn)         MINIMAX_KEY           platform.minimax.io / platform.minimaxi.com
# Zhipu Z.ai (intl/cn)      ZHIPU_KEY             z.ai / open.bigmodel.cn
# Moonshot Kimi             MOONSHOT_KEY          platform.moonshot.ai
# Alibaba Qwen              QWEN_KEY              dashscope.console.aliyun.com
# Custom router/endpoint    CUSTOM_KEY            depends on your setup

# ANTHROPIC_KEY=sk-ant-...
# DEEPSEEK_KEY=sk-...
# MINIMAX_KEY=sk-...
# ZHIPU_KEY=...
# MOONSHOT_KEY=sk-...
# QWEN_KEY=sk-...
